  "key": "C# minor",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "You know that feeling coming in your soul when you tell yourself you're not good at all You know it, we all know it, keep your shit secure Don't lose the love and light your love for yourself Don't lose the love and light your love for yourself It's harder to see you when you're dark in your own view When you can't see what's right through Yeah, don't lose that love for you Don't lose the love that you have for yourself When you're just a little baby flowing in the world You love every interaction, no matter the present This is your judgement day, yeah, that's the real you Find a way to get back to that time When you felt like you were a dime, cause you know you are You only get to see you, so you better find out true When they love their baby, it's how we all make it through the night Cause when you come back there all for yourself Because you know you deserve it When you're really being you, all around you shines through That view of you baby, it shines through for all to see So don't lose the love for you inside of you Don't lose that view, that love for you It's what you need to pass it on and love it to the next generation Don't take it in, protect it like a secret",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 7.940000057220459,
      "text": "You know that feeling coming in your soul when you tell yourself you're not good at all",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 14.699999809265137,
      "text": "You know it, we all know it, keep your shit secure",
      "start": 8.4399995803833
    },
    {
      "end": 21.440000534057617,
      "text": "Don't lose the love and light your love for yourself",
      "start": 15.039999961853027
    },
    {
      "end": 29.65999984741211,
      "text": "Don't lose the love and light your love for yourself",
      "start": 22.760000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 35.040000915527344,
      "text": "It's harder to see you when you're dark in your own view",
      "start": 29.8799991607666
    },
    {
      "end": 38.79999923706055,
      "text": "When you can't see what's right through",
      "start": 35.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 44.63999938964844,
      "text": "Yeah, don't lose that love for you",
      "start": 40.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 53.2400016784668,
      "text": "Don't lose the love that you have for yourself",
      "start": 45.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 57.220001220703125,
      "text": "When you're just a little baby flowing in the world",
      "start": 53.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 61.2599983215332,
      "text": "You love every interaction, no matter the present",
      "start": 57.220001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 65.08000183105469,
      "text": "This is your judgement day, yeah, that's the real you",
      "start": 61.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 70.58000183105469,
      "text": "Find a way to get back to that time",
      "start": 65.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 74.33999633789062,
      "text": "When you felt like you were a dime, cause you know you are",
      "start": 70.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 77.9000015258789,
      "text": "You only get to see you, so you better find out true",
      "start": 74.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 84.55999755859375,
      "text": "When they love their baby, it's how we all make it through the night",
      "start": 77.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 91.33999633789062,
      "text": "Cause when you come back there all for yourself",
      "start": 84.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 95.08000183105469,
      "text": "Because you know you deserve it",
      "start": 91.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 102.41999816894531,
      "text": "When you're really being you, all around you shines through",
      "start": 95.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 114.62000274658203,
      "text": "That view of you baby, it shines through for all to see",
      "start": 106.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 122.19999694824219,
      "text": "So don't lose the love for you inside of you",
      "start": 114.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 129.32000732421875,
      "text": "Don't lose that view, that love for you",
      "start": 122.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 133.1999969482422,
      "text": "It's what you need to pass it on and love it to the next generation",
      "start": 129.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 137.0399932861328,
      "text": "Don't take it in, protect it like a secret",
      "start": 133.8000030517578
    }
  ],
